                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.H.5.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 69, paragraph 5</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="italic">Sub-paragraph b:</hi> Add after the words “charitable
                    purposes” the words “other than property acquired or established during military
                    occupation”.</p>
                <p>Add a sub-paragraph as follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Sub-paragraphs <hi rend="italic">a</hi> and <hi rend="italic">c</hi> of
                            the present Article shall not apply to Ethiopia.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
